ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T08:40:36.000Z","msg":"明明周圍都係水，化淡得，地下抽上來又得，政府死都話唔夠水，要上面買水，仲要年年都倒唔少走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5e67d2d768c87c68b5197a2c827e69be10e7e8f","tid":805862,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:15:33.000Z","msg":"你估政府唔知咩 要諗知理由買東江水咋嘛"},{"pid":"23afcd284214fe40db71ee0414c24719b351cd32","tid":805862,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:25:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b17de16698ad2b1dee79cfbb575d2a7f4c34484e","tid":805862,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:28:22.000Z","msg":"要買東江水 不研究了"},{"pid":"3335eb84e2bf5077e9d127c4494a2963692183d6","tid":805862,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:34:10.000Z","msg":"淨係海水化淡已經係可行<br />\n誠哥又有投資<br />\n政府都唔推行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c79c8448b01a1fd174d962f353d9d28938ababc","tid":805862,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b60b2305d194d5d156b85394d4b21e804689d3b","tid":805862,"uid":550,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T08:06:00.000Z","msg":"香港落雨量算多 未必要花咁多錢開採地下水<br />\n三面環海我地發展海水化淡隨時仲化算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T09:35:28.000Z","msg":"Why not both<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港又唔係冇咁嘅錢/地去做晒兩樣嘢<br />\n<br />\n新界大撚把棕地/閒置嘅私人土地 政府有心做的話肯泵水實做到"},{"pid":"963dcb1b1213624aa73cd7c19aee611fbbdd0681","tid":805862,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T11:07:41.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"a74ebefe1b176392366a4225a96334bc27a7b3f6","tid":805862,"uid":57023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7488f20c9fa2750d8948f9e2ab9a906cad4ae254","